{"type": "article", "id": 16169, "title": "脸盲种族的 18 条日常问句 | 好奇心研究所", "description": "有本事连自己都不认识。", "date": "2015-10-17T06:23:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 17316, "name": "脸盲"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 36, "praise_count": 103, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071301203WE9LtyiRgmuYqP8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1.  我们见过吗？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130110zmuDwqvo85E6C3XH.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.69387755\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>2.  我们没见过？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143531ZsPpcoheNSyvqYr4.gif\" width=\"359\" height=\"228\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.63509749\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>3.  根据声音/发型/衣服/鞋/名字……我们真的（没）见过？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130111tRuTqvz6Xb0iG8oK.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>4.  居然是 TA ？！</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071301123Z961xnMLc4tzFDQ.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>５.  如何区分王珞丹和白百何？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> </strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713011334nRsreF2HoZ6gDP.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.97149644\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>６.  徐峥为什么在主持？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071301141UMRe7ShWznDGEpJ.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.73942094\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>７.  郭达怎么变这么帅？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130114BouMnsLR5EY3UX1Z.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66612903\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>８.  “康康哥哥……”“我是大竣……”“大竣哥哥……”“…………我叫康康…………” </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>“妈，我小时候也这样？＂</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130115cKvIDFoUtS27QAjY.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.55517241\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>９.  没事写那么多角色干吗？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143531IeDV7G90tfjao8h4.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"481\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.962\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>10.  这漫画里的人真的就是发型不一样啊？</strong><span><strong>！</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130115RaXNGuBxwpHZvjCU.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>11.  聊天进行半小时。（谁？）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143532ZhWNSi0xBwRvFqP7.gif\" width=\"261\" height=\"282\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"1.08045977\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>12.  “你好啊，</strong><span><strong>好久不见。</strong></span><strong>”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>“你好你好。”（谁？）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261435411iIMndCJ5RGtpa7D.gif\" width=\"425\" height=\"239\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.56235294\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>13.  保持微笑。（谁？）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130116Mbr0J8qFtxmBTWhG.jpg\" title=\"２\" alt=\"２\" data-ratio=\"0.75090909\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>14.  好像是亲戚/老师/领导啊。应不应该打招呼！？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130116ZPstg3Hnf5LKxBlD.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>15.  毕业照背后怎么可以没有名牌？！我怎么去参加高中聚会？！</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130117gq2UnDPT9bKFtAyC.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5525\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>16.  为什么完全分不清 NBA 球星，但一露面就知道是哪个韩国偶像团体？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>OR 为什么完全分不清 EXO，但一露面就知道是哪个球星？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130118pdDm5onWEHyA4wfG.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>17.  王思聪还不专一？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071301195Y39jTKmhveAa8RJ.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66621622\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>18.  谁让 TA 长得不够美？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130119he6Brw5VAkuHUWTX.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.48545455\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em></em></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em>好奇心研究所</em></a><em>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}